<h2>5. What can I do to make things better?</h2>

<p>It might not feel like there’s anything you can do now. Everything might just feel awful. I get that, I’ve been in those dark places. But sometimes, and I think often, there are little things we can do to make things a tiny bit better.
</p>

<ul>
    <li>Can you get a glass of water or a cup of tea? (or whatever your choice beverage is)</li>
    <li>Can you get some sleep?</li>
    <li>Can you eat something?</li>

</ul>

<p>Of course these things aren’t going to solve the problem or the bad thing, but they may help you be able to deal with it a little better. If you’re finding it hard to do things then you might find <a href="/blogs/6-Tips-on-doing-tasks-when-you-don’t-want-to">6 Tips on doing tasks when you don't want to</a> useful.</p>


